The changes made to `src/vs/sessions/browser/actions/vscodeActions.ts` and `src/vs/sessions/browser/openInVSCodeUtils.ts` are logically correct and well-tested. However, there are a few improvements that can be made to ensure the code is more maintainable and adheres to best practices.

